{"tid":1564822,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟我地交咁多稅，換黎d咩？","createTime":"2019-09-13T02:16:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T02:17:44.000Z","uid":221360,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ce105869ee657a64dc33a32afebb31e76ca902db","tid":1564822,"uid":221360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T02:16:43.000Z","msg":"利申：本人出社會幾年姐，人工25k交稅都唔多，只係鄧果班中產慘姐。<br />\n<br />\n大家有冇諗過？你地年年交稅交咁多，政府點樣回報你地？<br />\n－ 拎晒d錢捐比中共；<br />\n－ 幫中共填海，等多d新移民有屋住；<br />\n－ 幫中共發展經濟（起鐵路呀，大橋呀，仲要樣樣都超額＋豆腐渣）；<br />\n－ 整燈柱check撚住你班蟻民；<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">－ 最嬲既係比錢養班淨係識打返市民既垃圾黑警</span></strong></span>，而家仲要加ot人工添。<br />\n。。。。。仲有大把講唔晒<br />\n之後咪派下錢比你地安慰下你地（仲要大把人冇添），當你地乞e咁撚囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n即係點？？大家交稅係應份既，係作為1個公民應要做既野。咁政府呢？我地交稅交咁多，特別係中產果d，交最多稅果班。但係呢福利又少，又驚比高產果班壟斷生意賺唔到錢，又要比錢養班廢老（我指係廢老呀，無腦果班）同新移民（無手無腳食綜緩果班）。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有陣時，真係覺得香港人好撚慘，完全就係工蟻黎，淨係可以付出唔會有收獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。有用既時候用盡你，冇用既時候食撚埋你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: brown;\">而家仲衰，好似比錢叫班狗黎咬返你咁，香港人係咪真係咁M？</span></strong></span><br />\n所以我決定，由今日開始唔會再交稅（雖然好少影響力唔大，但我覺得連呢少少錢都無必要比），直到香港變返真正既香港為止。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我知實有五毛話我冇圖講乜撚野都得架，sorry i dont care wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我冇叫你地唔交稅呀，自己諗下應唔應該交啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港  時代革命<br />\n五大訴求  缺一不可</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"b1c7236d433a9ee760371459860b6995d79fc28d","tid":1564822,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T02:17:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b67cfb7adeb4619f579f3018315a72448a0b5ceb","tid":1564822,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T02:17:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"}]}